description:
This #short clip from the message, “Why is Jesus Our Ultimate Vaccine for Sin?” https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuqnDLIgqnE by Pastor Mark Finley explains that the resurrection of Christ is the ultimate life-changing event, and Jesus is the leading and only solution to all our sins.

Jesus encourages us to believe that He loves and cares for us, that there is hope for us, and that He will deliver us from the virus of sin. Watch the video to hear Pastor Finley talk about the assurance we can have if we believe and trust in God, even when we can’t comprehend what’s happening around us.
